data.name: Supporter_Instructions_Label.Text
data.value: To get supporter code donate $2 or more. Supporter code is for a lifetime. You will get your supporter code on your PayPal email. It may take up to 24h (probably less, may be even instant). If you didn't get your code, mail me at pionner@smartmoose.org. Please, do not share it (publicly shared codes may get banned).

data.name: www_main_content.Text
data.value:
Welcome to {server_name}!
To play please join IP: {server_ip}:{server_port}

This is sample website. You can use HTML tags here.



For example, you can put some screenshots here:


Note, that 7DSM WebServer doesn't support own images hosting yet, so you need to put them somewhere else, eg. imgur
Also please note that current implementation may be very CPU hungry. Avoid using it on big servers.
